      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS for optimal volumetric efficiency. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, maintaining the communicative feedback this chassis is known for. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and a precision valve clearance adjustment. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals remain sharp and track-ready.",
